title: 2022 Act to Ratify the Sanjowor Convention on Diplomatic Relations
content:
**AN ACT**
*of the Congress of the Bayer Free State*
reference code ACT_2022_00002

*Be it enacted by this Congress*, That, on this twelfth day in the month of March, in the year two thousand and twenty-two and forever after, the Convention on Diplomatic Relations signed by the delegations of the Bayer Free State and the Democratic Republic of Sanjowor shall hereby be approved.
